1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:40,980
=Cinta Di Luar Kubur=
(Diadaptasi daripada novel oleh Li Qingran)

2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episod 15=

3
00:01:49,030 --> 00:01:49,870
Bapa,

4
00:01:50,670 --> 00:01:52,060
adakah awak menjauhkan saya selama ini

5
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:54,110
untuk roh jahat itu?

6
00:01:55,670 --> 00:01:57,270
Semua adik beradik saya mati muda.

7
00:01:57,670 --> 00:01:58,860
Anda tahu sebabnya selama ini.

8
00:01:59,270 --> 00:02:00,300
Memandangkan anda tahu itu,

9
00:02:00,860 --> 00:02:02,420
kenapa terus berurusan dengan roh jahat?

10
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:03,750
Semuanya untuk memuaskan hati

11
00:02:03,750 --> 00:02:04,830
keinginan anda sendiri.

12
00:02:06,390 --> 00:02:07,230
Bapa,

13
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:09,550
bagaimana anda boleh terus melakukan ini?

14
00:02:09,950 --> 00:02:10,990
Didorong oleh roh jahat,

15
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:13,070
anda tidak kisah pun anak-anak anda

16
00:02:13,070 --> 00:02:13,910
telah dimakan olehnya.

17
00:02:16,390 --> 00:02:17,460
Saya bapa awak.

18
00:02:18,070 --> 00:02:19,336
Awak rasa saya buat ini untuk siapa?

19
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:22,020
Di Mahkamah Diraja,

20
00:02:22,790 --> 00:02:24,070
kami sentiasa dipandang rendah,

21
00:02:24,390 --> 00:02:25,620
jadi kami dihalau ke sini.

22
00:02:26,460 --> 00:02:28,300
Jika saya tidak tawar-menawar
dengan roh jahat itu,

23
00:02:29,270 --> 00:02:31,790
bagaimana kita boleh bangkit semula?

24
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:32,860
Dan bagaimana anda boleh

25
00:02:33,270 --> 00:02:34,740
pernah menjadi

26
00:02:35,110 --> 00:02:36,300
Paderi Muda?

27
00:02:36,300 --> 00:02:37,140
Bapa,

28
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:39,550
bangkit semula adalah keinginan anda,

29
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:41,020
bukan milik saya

30
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:42,860
atau adik beradik saya'.

31
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:44,620
Sejak awak

32
00:02:44,620 --> 00:02:45,510
telah mengkhianati Cangshen,

33
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:47,790
Saya patut letak jawatan kerana malu

34
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:49,680
dan meninggalkan Mahkamah Diraja.

35
00:02:52,390 --> 00:02:53,460
Bagaimana anda boleh berkata begitu?

36
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:55,300
mengarut?

37
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:56,740
letak jawatan?

38
00:02:58,070 --> 00:02:59,390
Adakah adik-beradik anda

39
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:00,620
mati sia-sia?

40
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:02,350
Kematian mereka bukan kerana saya.

41
00:03:02,990 --> 00:03:04,140
Mereka mati kerana awak.

42
00:03:05,390 --> 00:03:06,230
Guru Yili'er,

43
00:03:07,230 --> 00:03:08,620
awak kata Luda bangkit sejauh ini

44
00:03:09,350 --> 00:03:10,990
kerana kamu telah berurusan dengan roh jahat.

45
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:12,700
Saya tidak fikir begitu.

46
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:15,340
Mungkin sebaliknya.

47
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:17,510
Mungkin Song Xingyu melihat lama dahulu

48
00:03:17,510 --> 00:03:18,460
betapa tidak puas hati anda

49
00:03:20,390 --> 00:03:21,799
dan bagaimana anda cuba menjadikan anak anda

50
00:03:21,810 --> 00:03:22,460
Imam Besar.

51
00:03:23,020 --> 00:03:24,140
Jadi, dia gunakan awak.

52
00:03:37,950 --> 00:03:39,020
Jika itu benar,

53
00:03:40,230 --> 00:03:41,180
kemudian saya

54
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:43,420
bunuh anak saya sendiri

55
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:46,740
dengan tangan saya sendiri?

56
00:03:54,230 --> 00:03:55,180
Jika tiada apa-apa lagi,

57
00:03:55,830 --> 00:03:57,110
Saya akan balik dan berehat dahulu.

58
00:03:59,270 --> 00:04:00,580
Tontonan lewat malam ini

59
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:02,270
telah benar-benar meletihkan saya.

60
00:04:03,830 --> 00:04:05,860
Anak-anak saya...

61
00:04:23,670 --> 00:04:24,510
pernah dengar?

62
00:04:24,910 --> 00:04:26,740
Malam tadi, di Rumah Yili'er,

63
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:27,670
semua khazanah mereka

64
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:29,380
hilang semalaman.

65
00:04:30,710 --> 00:04:31,820
Sayang sekali.

66
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:32,950
Sesungguhnya.

67
00:04:33,090 --> 00:04:33,940
Menjelang pagi,

68
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,300
gundik dan hamba

69
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,820
- Tuan-tuan.
- semua telah pergi.

70
00:04:37,260 --> 00:04:38,230
Sekarang,

71
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,500
hanya Master Yili'er

72
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:40,653
dan Tuan Muda Luda kekal.

73
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:42,260
Tuan Muda yang lain

74
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:43,940
turut lemas.

75
00:04:52,180 --> 00:04:53,420
Saya bercakap dengan Ayah malam tadi.

76
00:04:55,180 --> 00:04:56,030
Dia akan kembali bersama saya

77
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:57,003
ke Ibu Kota untuk menebus.

78
00:04:57,910 --> 00:04:59,260
Dia tidak akan kembali ke Youzhou.

79
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:02,670
Anda begitu mempercayai Cangshen?

80
00:05:03,380 --> 00:05:04,220
Cangshen

81
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:05,740
adalah, sebenarnya, sejenis iman.

82
00:05:09,110 --> 00:05:10,230
Anda juga mempunyai keyakinan.

83
00:05:11,150 --> 00:05:11,990
Anda sepatutnya tahu ini.

84
00:05:12,710 --> 00:05:14,030
Apabila iman seseorang cukup teguh,

85
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,230
ia boleh menandingi

86
00:05:15,230 --> 00:05:16,350
semua senjata di dunia.

87
00:05:17,260 --> 00:05:18,100
Kuasa Cangshen

88
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:20,120
terletak pada satu kepercayaan yang dikongsi oleh berjuta-juta.

89
00:05:24,790 --> 00:05:25,630
Tujuh belas,

90
00:05:26,710 --> 00:05:27,433
anda pernah percaya

91
00:05:27,444 --> 00:05:28,573
dalam Aphorisms of Cangshen.

92
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:30,110
Kenapa sekarang...

93
00:05:30,110 --> 00:05:30,950
Dalam Aforisme,

94
00:05:31,316 --> 00:05:32,429
Rahmat terbesar Cangshen

95
00:05:32,977 --> 00:05:34,403
adalah untuk menyebarkan barisan Rakyat Chong

96
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:36,300
ke setiap pelusuk dunia.

97
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:38,740
Anda berarak ke selatan dan merampas

98
00:05:39,253 --> 00:05:40,633
Tanah Liang yang hebat dan penduduknya.

99
00:05:41,740 --> 00:05:43,380
Adakah ini yang diminta oleh iman anda daripada anda?

100
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,990
Saya tahu bahawa antara dua negara

101
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:51,690
terletak kebencian yang mendalam.

102
00:05:52,180 --> 00:05:53,020
Tetapi saya harap

103
00:05:53,470 --> 00:05:54,420
lebih ramai orang Liang

104
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,600
akan datang menyembah Cangshen

105
00:05:55,837 --> 00:05:56,986
dan menjadi orang Cangshen.

106
00:05:57,910 --> 00:05:59,110
Setiap orang harus melakukan bahagian mereka sendiri,

107
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:00,590
dengan tiada lagi perselisihan.

108
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:04,510
Tujuh belas,

109
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:06,030
pernahkah anda terfikir

110
00:06:06,910 --> 00:06:08,150
macam mana saya kenal awak semalam?

111
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:10,700
Imam Muda,

112
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:13,620
kami tidak pernah berkawan.

113
00:06:14,790 --> 00:06:16,150
Suatu hari nanti, kita mungkin menjadi musuh.

114
00:06:16,940 --> 00:06:17,780
Jadi,

115
00:06:18,150 --> 00:06:18,990
mari berpisah di sini.

116
00:06:20,230 --> 00:06:21,110
Jaga diri.

117
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:00,810
Salam, Tuanku.

118
00:07:02,260 --> 00:07:03,180
Awak bergegas balik.

119
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:04,426
Ada apa-apa yang salah dengan Her Grace?

120
00:07:04,790 --> 00:07:05,740
Tuanku,

121
00:07:05,740 --> 00:07:07,033
Song Xingyu dilihat di Youzhou.

122
00:07:08,790 --> 00:07:10,110
Jadi, Yang Mulia pergi ke Youzhou

123
00:07:10,550 --> 00:07:11,670
kerana dia.

124
00:07:14,710 --> 00:07:16,420
Adakah Yang Mulia menangkap Song Xingyu?

125
00:07:16,910 --> 00:07:17,750
Dia melarikan diri.

126
00:07:19,670 --> 00:07:20,510
Difahamkan.

127
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:21,700
Tuanku,

128
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:23,670
semangat pun ada

129
00:07:23,670 --> 00:07:24,520
di sisinya.

130
00:07:24,530 --> 00:07:25,503
Identitinya tidak diketahui.

131
00:07:26,030 --> 00:07:28,030
Adakah anda pasti ia bukan manusia?

132
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,060
Ia adalah semangat

133
00:07:29,060 --> 00:07:30,046
dengan kekuatan semangat yang kuat.

134
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,460
Naan!

135
00:07:52,940 --> 00:07:53,780
Turunkan saya.

136
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:56,230
Beritahu saya di mana Song Xingyu berada,

137
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,340
dan saya akan lepaskan awak.

138
00:07:58,030 --> 00:07:58,910
saya tak tahu.

139
00:07:58,910 --> 00:07:59,860
Saya benar-benar tidak tahu.

140
00:08:00,940 --> 00:08:02,150
Saya percaya anda tidak tahu.

141
00:08:02,710 --> 00:08:03,710
Tetapi Yang Berdaulat tidak akan.

142
00:08:07,710 --> 00:08:09,300
Baik, saya akan bercakap.

143
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:11,550
Turunkan saya dulu.

144
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:34,980
Awak...

145
00:08:49,710 --> 00:08:51,110
Salam, Tuanku.

146
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:53,260
Mengapa anda dalam keadaan panik?

147
00:08:54,430 --> 00:08:55,380
Tuanku,

148
00:08:55,860 --> 00:08:57,430
semasa saya menjalankan tugas penguatkuasaan undang-undang,

149
00:08:57,590 --> 00:08:59,740
Saya terserempak dengan Song Xingyu.

150
00:09:00,110 --> 00:09:01,310
Saya melakukan semua yang saya mampu

151
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:02,890
untuk menghentikan Song Xingyu,

152
00:09:02,890 --> 00:09:04,140
tetapi dia masih melarikan diri.

153
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,260
Saya cemas

154
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:08,190
kerana…

155
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:09,540
Kerana saya mahu

156
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:10,660
untuk melaporkan berita ini

157
00:09:10,830 --> 00:09:11,670
kepada anda sekali gus.

158
00:09:15,990 --> 00:09:16,830
Tolong percayakan saya.

159
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:17,950
Ini...

160
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:18,790
Saya mendapat

161
00:09:18,900 --> 00:09:19,740
perkara ini

162
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:21,110
dari tempat persembunyian Song Xingyu.

163
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:22,380
Tolong terima.

164
00:09:22,740 --> 00:09:24,190
Tolong percayakan saya.

165
00:09:32,990 --> 00:09:34,230
melutut. Cepat.

166
00:09:34,430 --> 00:09:35,270
Berlutut, sekarang.

167
00:09:38,350 --> 00:09:39,190
melutut.

168
00:09:40,070 --> 00:09:40,910
Berlutut, sekarang.

169
00:09:41,230 --> 00:09:42,310
Sambut Tangan Kanan.

170
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:43,310
dengan pantas.

171
00:09:50,350 --> 00:09:51,350
Tolong maafkan dia.

172
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:53,310
Dia adalah roh yang baru terbentuk.

173
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:54,500
Dia masih keliru,

174
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:55,430
tidak mengetahui peraturan.

175
00:09:55,430 --> 00:09:56,270
Dia...

176
00:10:06,140 --> 00:10:07,070
(Tangan Kanan?)

177
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:08,860
(Adakah dia orang bawahan Simu?)

178
00:10:19,830 --> 00:10:20,843
Selamat jalan Tuanku.

179
00:10:27,190 --> 00:10:28,443
Setiap kali saya melihat Tangan Kanan,

180
00:10:28,950 --> 00:10:29,790
ia mengalir pergi

181
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:31,500
sepuluh tahun kegembiraan yang saya simpan.

182
00:10:31,950 --> 00:10:32,790
Beraninya awak

183
00:10:33,230 --> 00:10:34,310
tengok Tangan Kanan?

184
00:10:34,590 --> 00:10:35,430
Adakah Tangan Kanan

185
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,190
sangat penting?

186
00:10:37,590 --> 00:10:38,540
Sudah tentu.

187
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:40,950
Dia hanya rendah diri

188
00:10:40,950 --> 00:10:41,790
kepada Rahmat-Nya.

189
00:10:41,950 --> 00:10:43,310
Dia yang paling boleh dipercayai

190
00:10:43,310 --> 00:10:44,230
kepada Rahmat-Nya.

191
00:10:47,230 --> 00:10:48,230
Yang paling boleh dipercayai.

192
00:10:51,230 --> 00:10:52,070
Dia dikenali

193
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,860
Rahmatnya selama berabad-abad.

194
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:54,710
Mereka berdua

195
00:10:54,710 --> 00:10:55,990
bergantung pada dan hormati

196
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:56,830
antara satu sama lain;

197
00:10:56,830 --> 00:10:58,380
jantung mereka berdegup serentak.

198
00:10:58,620 --> 00:10:59,460
Bak kata pepatah,

199
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:01,110
ikatan mereka berjalan dalam.

200
00:11:02,690 --> 00:11:03,530
Dalam Kekosongan,

201
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:04,390
semua roh berfikir

202
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,410
mereka sepasang.

203
00:11:05,430 --> 00:11:06,270
Selama bertahun-tahun ini,

204
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:07,752
semasa Yang Mulia tiada,

205
00:11:07,763 --> 00:11:08,830
tangan Kanan dikendalikan

206
00:11:09,190 --> 00:11:10,540
Dunia Roh seperti pemerintah bersama.

207
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:12,620
Malah Tangan Kiri tidak mempunyai penghormatan itu.

208
00:11:13,190 --> 00:11:14,990
Tangan Kanan benar-benar model

209
00:11:14,990 --> 00:11:15,830
untuk semua roh lelaki.

210
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:18,190
Daripada bunyinya,

211
00:11:19,310 --> 00:11:21,123
Tangan Kanan dan Rahmat-Nya
agak rapat.

212
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,260
Adakah Her Grace menyukainya?

213
00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:26,620
Sudah tentu.

214
00:11:27,070 --> 00:11:28,260
Tangan Kanan itu kacak,

215
00:11:28,430 --> 00:11:29,270
berkebolehan tinggi,

216
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:30,780
dan benar-benar berbakti kepadanya.

217
00:11:30,950 --> 00:11:32,230
Dia jatuh cinta padanya lama dahulu.

218
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:34,110
Jika tidak, mengapa dia mempercayainya

219
00:11:34,350 --> 00:11:35,900
dengan Kekosongan?

220
00:11:39,020 --> 00:11:39,860
Jika begitu,

221
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:42,070
Tangan Kanan adalah masalah.

222
00:11:42,350 --> 00:11:43,190
Ya, ya.

223
00:11:43,190 --> 00:11:44,140
Dia sukar untuk dikendalikan.

224
00:11:44,380 --> 00:11:45,230
Jika anda pergi ke Void,

225
00:11:45,230 --> 00:11:46,350
jangan marah dia.

226
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:47,390
Atau anda akan berakhir

227
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,500
sedang dimusnahkan.

228
00:11:50,950 --> 00:11:51,790
Itu tidak betul.

229
00:11:52,470 --> 00:11:54,110
Anda telah membuang saya dari landasan.

230
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:55,780
Kenapa awak banyak bertanya?

231
00:11:56,540 --> 00:11:57,380
Ayuh.

232
00:11:57,540 --> 00:11:59,260
Saya tidak tahu di mana Song Xingyu berada.

233
00:11:59,710 --> 00:12:00,620
Tetapi

234
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:01,900
anda perlu mengikuti saya

235
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:03,190
kembali ke Kekosongan.

236
00:12:08,070 --> 00:12:08,910
apa?

237
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:16,860
(Pewangi)

238
00:12:16,860 --> 00:12:21,700
(Wain)

239
00:12:30,430 --> 00:12:31,740
Kenapa awak pergi bersendirian?

240
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:33,740
Awak tak tunggu saya pun.

241
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:41,620
Jangan minum berlebihan hari ini.

242
00:12:42,350 --> 00:12:43,190
Kali terakhir…

243
00:12:43,350 --> 00:12:44,470
Sebaik sahaja kuasa semangat saya kembali,

244
00:12:44,860 --> 00:12:46,140
Saya akan membuat anda menderita untuk itu.

245
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:49,900
Saya sudah cukup menderita

246
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:50,830
di Dunia Fana.

247
00:12:51,590 --> 00:12:52,430
Nampaknya

248
00:12:52,810 --> 00:12:53,660
anda akan minta saya sampel

249
00:12:53,660 --> 00:12:54,500
penderitaan Void.

250
00:12:57,380 --> 00:12:58,740
Jika anda berkeras mahu menghukum saya,

251
00:13:00,660 --> 00:13:01,830
izinkan saya menggunakan ini

252
00:13:03,430 --> 00:13:04,270
untuk menebus kesalahan.

253
00:13:12,230 --> 00:13:13,165
Anda tiada lima deria

254
00:13:13,176 --> 00:13:13,910
di tembok kota.

255
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:15,583
Perkara berbeza sekarang.

256
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:17,710
Walaupun anda tidak dapat merasainya,

257
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:19,830
anda boleh menghidu harumannya.

258
00:13:30,990 --> 00:13:32,500
